HEADWORD: Affirmatively
<hw>Af*firm"a*tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an affirmative
manner; on the affirmative side of a question; in the affirmative; --
opposed to <ant>negatively</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
